<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">当我年轻时</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">When I was yong</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">常听收音机</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">I’d listen to the radio</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">等待心爱的歌曲</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Waiting for my favorite songs</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">听到播放时便随声歌唱</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">When they played I’d sing along</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">这使我欢畅</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">It made me smile</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">当我年轻时</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">When I was yong</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">常听收音机</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">I’d listen to the radio</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">等待心爱的歌曲</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Waiting for my favorite songs</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">听到播放时便随声歌唱</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">When they played I’d sing along</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">这使我欢畅</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">It made me smile</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">人生中最美好的珍藏，正是那些往日时光。</span></p>
